title: Sound On: Democrats Plan Biden Agenda Vote
itunes:title: Sound On: Democrats Plan Biden Agenda Vote
description:
Bloomberg Washington Correspondent Joe Mathieu delivers insight and analysis on the latest headlines from the White House and Capitol Hill, including conversations with influential lawmakers and key figures in politics and policy.


Guests: Congressman Sean Casten of Illinois, Congressman Warren Davidson of Ohio, Congresswoman Pramila Jayapal of Washington, Congresswoman Ayanna Pressley of Massachusetts, Bloomberg Government
